    "solution": "from urllib.parse import urlparse, parse_qs\n\nurl = 'https://example.com:8080/path/to/page?id=123&name=alice#section'\n\n# 解析 URL\nparsed = urlparse(url)\n\nprint(f'协议: {parsed.scheme}')\nprint(f'主机: {parsed.netloc}')\nprint(f'端口: {parsed.port}')\nprint(f'路径: {parsed.path}')\nprint(f'查询: {parsed.query}')\nprint(f'锚点: {parsed.fragment}')\n\n# 解析查询参数\nparams = parse_qs(parsed.query)\nprint(f'参数: {params}')\nprint(f'id值: {params.get(\"id\")}')",
