    "starter_code": "import pandas as pd\n\n# 创建两个数据集\ndf1 = pd.DataFrame({\n    'id': [1, 2, 3],\n    'name': ['Alice', 'Bob', 'Charlie'],\n    'dept_id': [101, 102, 101]\n})\n\ndf2 = pd.DataFrame({\n    'dept_id': [101, 102, 103],\n    'department': ['IT', 'HR', 'Sales'],\n    'location': ['Beijing', 'Shanghai', 'Guangzhou']\n})\n\n# 内连接合并\nmerged = # 你的代码\n\nprint('合并结果:')\nprint(merged)",
    "solution": "import pandas as pd\n\n# 创建两个数据集\ndf1 = pd.DataFrame({\n    'id': [1, 2, 3],\n    'name': ['Alice', 'Bob', 'Charlie'],\n    'dept_id': [101, 102, 101]\n})\n\ndf2 = pd.DataFrame({\n    'dept_id': [101, 102, 103],\n    'department': ['IT', 'HR', 'Sales'],\n    'location': ['Beijing', 'Shanghai', 'Guangzhou']\n})\n\n# 内连接合并\nmerged = pd.merge(df1, df2, on='dept_id', how='inner')\n\nprint('内连接结果:')\nprint(merged)\n\n# 左连接\nmerged_left = pd.merge(df1, df2, on='dept_id', how='left')\nprint('\\n左连接结果:')\nprint(merged_left)",
