    "starter_code": "import cv2\nimport numpy as np\n\n# 创建一个简单的测试图像\n# 实际使用时替换为 cv2.imread('image.jpg')\nimage = np.zeros((200, 300, 3), dtype=np.uint8)\nimage[:] = (100, 150, 200)  # 蓝色背景\n\n# 绘制矩形\ncv2.rectangle(image, (50, 50), (150, 150), (0, 255, 0), 2)\n\n# 绘制文字\ncv2.putText(image, 'Hello!', (80, 100), cv2.FONT_HERSHEY_SIMPLEX, 1, (255, 255, 255), 2)\n\n# 显示图像信息\nprint(f'图像形状: {image.shape}')\nprint(f'图像大小: {image.size}')\nprint(f'数据类型: {image.dtype}')",
    "solution": "import cv2\nimport numpy as np\n\n# 创建一个简单的测试图像\nimage = np.zeros((200, 300, 3), dtype=np.uint8)\nimage[:] = (100, 150, 200)  # 蓝色背景\n\n# 绘制矩形\ncv2.rectangle(image, (50, 50), (150, 150), (0, 255, 0), 2)\n\n# 绘制文字\ncv2.putText(image, 'Hello!', (80, 100), cv2.FONT_HERSHEY_SIMPLEX, 1, (255, 255, 255), 2)\n\n# 显示图像信息\nprint(f'图像形状: {image.shape}')\nprint(f'图像大小: {image.size}')\nprint(f'数据类型: {image.dtype}')\nprint(f'图像尺寸: {image.shape[1]}x{image.shape[0]}')\n\n# 保存图像\ncv2.imwrite('test_image.png', image)\nprint('图像已保存为 test_image.png')",
